    <thetext>If a test takes over 10 min. the ManagedTestSuite interrupts the main test thread. In case the thread is in an operation that does not check the interrupted flag a subsequent test may throw an InterruptedException later.

To avoid that ManagedTestSuite.endTest() should clear the interrupted flag.</thetext>
